Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:41.31,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶如扯碎的雲般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:44.34,ED-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,looking for 見つけて
